      <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
         <head>Provenance</head>
         <p> The papers of the Francis Lewis Cardozo family were given to the
		  Library of Congress by Margaret Cardozo Holmes, Elizabeth Cardozo Barker,
		  Frances Cardozo Payne, Catherine Cardozo Lewis, and Meta Cardozo Hurley in
		  1976.</p>
      </acqinfo>
